[2008-04-09]
Version 0.4.11.2                            "How far the sky,
                                             how cold the night,
                                             how still the flowing river.
                                             How sharp the air --
                                             so pure the light --
                                             beneath Orion's quiver.
                                             Beneath the frozen, staring,
